org.apache.river.test.spec.activation.util

Class FakeActivationID

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.rmi.activation.ActivationID
      • org.apache.river.test.spec.activation.util.FakeActivationID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, net.jini.security.proxytrust.TrustEquivalence

    public class FakeActivationID
extends ActivationID
implements net.jini.security.proxytrust.TrustEquivalence
    A fake implementation of the ActivationID class. It doesn't make real activation, only emulate it.
